Breville Group Limited (ASX: BRG) is an Australian company which sells electrical consumer products and home goods. It is based in Sydney.
The company owns several brands, including Breville (for some countries), Kambrook, Ronson, Sage by Heston Blumenthal, Solis, Gastroback, Stollar, Catler, Bork and Riviera&Bar. 
The company started as a small importer in 1957. They have been listed on the Australian stock exchange since 1999.
